    "Additionally, they should establish connections between various physical symbols and the rules acquired through symbolic AI.",
    "Here, a viable approach is to develop a formal logical language designed to encapsulate the exhaustive ontology of wireless concepts and articulate rules governing the functioning of wireless systems (and is the symbolic part here).",
